---
// Process Section
---

<section id="process" class="section-pad process-section">
  <div class="container-znatic">

    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">How We Work</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        A process built for<br />
        <em class="italic-accent">clarity &amp; craft</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-sub">
        Every project follows a deliberate rhythm — designed to reduce ambiguity,
        protect quality, and deliver results that exceed expectation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps with skeleton overlay -->
    <div class="process-wrapper">
      <div class="skeleton-steps" id="process-skeleton" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="skeleton skeleton-block" style="height:110px"></div>
        <div class="skeleton skeleton-block" style="height:110px"></div>
        <div class="skeleton skeleton-block" style="height:110px"></div>
        <div class="skeleton skeleton-block" style="height:110px"></div>
        <div class="skeleton skeleton-block" style="height:110px"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="proc-list reveal-stagger" id="process-content">

        <div class="proc-item">
          <div class="proc-left">
            <span class="proc-count">01</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proc-right">
            <p class="proc-phase">Discover</p>
            <h3 class="proc-title">Deep Discovery</h3>
            <p class="proc-desc">
              We immerse ourselves in your world — your goals, users, and
              market. A thorough discovery phase ensures every decision is grounded in insight.
            </p>
            <p class="proc-tags">Research · Briefing · Audit</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="proc-divider"></div>

        <div class="proc-item">
          <div class="proc-left">
            <span class="proc-count">02</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proc-right">
            <p class="proc-phase">Design</p>
            <h3 class="proc-title">Intentional Design</h3>
            <p class="proc-desc">
              From wireframes to high-fidelity prototypes, we craft interfaces
              with rigorous attention to hierarchy, aesthetics, and usability.
            </p>
            <p class="proc-tags">Wireframes · Prototypes · Design System</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="proc-divider"></div>

        <div class="proc-item">
          <div class="proc-left">
            <span class="proc-count">03</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proc-right">
            <p class="proc-phase">Build</p>
            <h3 class="proc-title">Precise Engineering</h3>
            <p class="proc-desc">
              Clean, maintainable code. We build with modern frameworks and
              best practices — performant, accessible, and built to last.
            </p>
            <p class="proc-tags">Development · QA · Integration</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="proc-divider"></div>

        <div class="proc-item">
          <div class="proc-left">
            <span class="proc-count">04</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proc-right">
            <p class="proc-phase">Launch</p>
            <h3 class="proc-title">Confident Launch</h3>
            <p class="proc-desc">
              A meticulous pre-launch checklist ensures a smooth, successful
              release. We handle deployment and post-launch monitoring.
            </p>
            <p class="proc-tags">Deployment · Testing · Monitoring</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="proc-divider"></div>

        <div class="proc-item">
          <div class="proc-left">
            <span class="proc-count">05</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proc-right">
            <p class="proc-phase">Support</p>
            <h3 class="proc-title">Ongoing Support</h3>
            <p class="proc-desc">
              Our relationship doesn’t end at launch. We provide continuous
              support, iteration, and strategic guidance as your product evolves.
            </p>
            <p class="proc-tags">Maintenance · Iteration · Strategy</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div><!-- /process-wrapper -->
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-soft);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-soft);
  }

  .process-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 200px;
  }

  .skeleton-steps {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    z-index: 2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* Editorial list */
  .proc-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .proc-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 88px 1fr;
    gap: 0 48px;
    padding: 52px 0;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .proc-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--color-border-soft);
  }

  /* Left: number */
  .proc-left {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .proc-count {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* Right: content */
  .proc-phase {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .proc-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.75rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .proc-desc {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.78;
    max-width: 54ch;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .proc-tags {
    font-size: 0.775rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* Section header shared */
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 72px;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-top: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .italic-accent {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .section-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.78;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .proc-item {
      grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr;
      gap: 0 24px;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
  }
</style>
